weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.model

Class WinningInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.model.WinningInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WinningInformation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains information about the closest prototypes regarding to the parent EmbeddedSpaceVector. The closest prototype with the same class is tracked. Same goes for the closest one with any different class. For them both, the distances are also provided. These values are utilized to compose the updates and to evaluate the costs of any particular proposed update.

    S
